{"tid":1686103,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"留意到無論勇武定和理非現場都有一個心態","createTime":"2019-11-01T02:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T07:05:43.000Z","uid":13936,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b75a365e762623e8b97f3fd9412970ccbdbda4a1","tid":1686103,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:29:09.000Z","msg":"僥倖心態<br />\n以為自己唔會成為其中一個被拉既人<br />\n所以落到場 九成時間 都係放鬆狀態<br />\n或者自以為安全距離 行行企企 抱觀望  叫下口號  有時間仲可以拎下手機睇下<br />\n見到狗 有部份人唔係即閃 更加唔係還拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而係企係到大叫死黑警 放人/ 死全家<br />\n究竟呢班人係街坊定係示威者  <br />\n如果你係街坊 但你全黑 Full gear<br />\n如果你係示威者 點解可以企係黑警面前大叫口號<br />\n<br />\n講到尾 大家都唔係進入戰爭  打仗 革命 MODE<br />\n試下真係革命打仗呀  離敵方一千米 我都淆到仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為戰爭無僥幸 落得場就預左大戰<br />\n請記住 反抗"},{"pid":"9f0383d867c5480753abd9b98a6ea0254364240b","tid":1686103,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:29:19.000Z","msg":"【突發】11月2活動需要大量文宣，你我都做到<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/erxDAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/erxDAS</a>"},{"pid":"ab7576c684b0956a7d5fd6c849afd1c5667c951f","tid":1686103,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d8d60c26bc87bf1f1fc42a8409974078740f0a","tid":1686103,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T06:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b08822cf4169a3ca031ce22687cf970b5246c0a","tid":1686103,"uid":307774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T06:39:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f03933abc97e5361be3a31e497fd33bc377b66f6","tid":1686103,"uid":77580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T06:42:58.000Z","msg":"危機意識唔夠"},{"pid":"0efab7223854981254255336d392472bfb48b5